Interface CodelistMapper

All Known Implementing Classes:
CodelistMapperImpl
public interface CodelistMapper

Codelist Mapper

MapStruct mapper for building gRPC requests to codelist service and transforming responses into lookup data. Handles extraction of codelist keys from study program data.

Version:
1.0.0
Author:
Jakub Pavlíček
